barrel_id = 9
barrel_name = "Archetype Railgun Spec"
barrel_desc = "[b]Archetype Barrel - Railgun Specialization[/b]
Change the innate nature of the gun. Ideally put this barrel at the first position.

Possible rolls:
[ul]
Gauss Rifle: High firerate and magazine, but lower damage.
Scatter Beam: Limited magazine size and high spread, but high projectile count.
Railcannon: Powerful oneshot wonder.
[/ul]"
